roleset.note: WADE-V NOTES: Frames file for 'wade' based on sentences in wsj. Verbnet entry 51.3.2, Framenet entry Self-motion. (from wade.01-v predicate notes)

example.name: metaphorical?
example.text: Geoffrey Goodfellow, who dropped out of high school back in the 1970s to manage a computer network at a California research firm, says: ``Old network hands have started to turn off the network because [they]-1 don't have time [*]-1 to wade through the muck.''
